  "description": "<i>Roland In Time</i> is a single player platform game in the Roland game series from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?company=Amstrad\">Amstrad</a>.<br><br>In this game Roland has been stranded on Earth by his evil nemesis Maestro. His intergalactic time travelling vehicle, the Anti-Matter Space-Time Run-ArounD', which looks a lot like a police box is powered by special crystals and these have been scattered throughout Earth's past and Earth's future.<br><br>The game's objective is to travel through all fifty three scenes / levels searching for these crystals and avoiding the baddies. \nThe player has at their disposal nine regeneration tanks, aka lives. \nIt can be played with either the keyboard or joystick.",
